          <description>Intermittent .NET host processes locking your build outputs? MSBuild&#x27;s node reuse feature causes file locking in complex build systems. Learn how MSBUILDDISABLENODEREUSE fixes years of sporadic build failures, why this optimization backfires, and when you should disable it.</description>
